    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 years or older

          -  Clinically confirmed viable pregnancy at the time of enrollment

          -  Clinically determined gestational age between 8 wks, 0 days and 22 wks, 0 days

          -  Referred or planning to undergo CVS or amniocentesis procedure due to risk of fetal
             aneuploidy based on protocol-specified clinical indicators

          -  Able to provide consent for participation using language appropriate forms and consent
             process

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - Invasive prenatal procedure (amniocentesis or CVS) performed prior to enrollment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
